      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/uks-close-bros-sells-wealth-business-oaktree-265-mln-deal-2024-09-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Close Brothers Group 已同意以高达 2 亿英镑（2.65 亿美元）的价格将其财富管理部门 Close Brothers Asset Management（CBAM）出售给私募股权公司 Oaktree Capital Management。]]></description>
